name: Denim Hand-painted Daisy Skirt
description:
This "Esprit" denim skirt is an original, one of a kind, hand-painted design with sprays of white petaled and yellow centered daisies. The daisies flow from the front of the skirt to the back. 
size 3/4
length 161/2"
2 pockets in front 
2 pockets in back with daisies
zipper front

name: Sunflowers!!mini-"vintage" denim skirt
description:
Sunflowers and more sunflowers on a mini-denim skirt. This is an original, one of a kind, hand-painted design. The painting was done on a Marlow Vintage skirt. It is so playful with the slight frill on the bottom, it can be worn any way you want. over leggings on cooler days. Sunflowers also on the back of the skirt. A happy looking skirt.
size 27
length 13"
2 front pockets

name: Butterfly Skirt, hand-painted, one of a kind
description:
Multi-colored butterflies have landed on this denim skirt. One peeks out of the front pocket and it looks as though it will fly off.
The butterflies create a sense of movement on the skirt and they are on the back also!

size; Junior 5
GLO brand skirt, pre-worn
131/4"length
2 front/2 back pockets

name: Denim Jacket, Hand-painted, One of a kInd
description:
This denim jacket is hand-painted and one of a kind and can dress up any outfit or just be awesome with anything you pair it with. The original design is a paisley pattern of gold, white and black. This Old Navy jacket is seeing it's best days!
size S (pre-worn)
light colored denim
Shoulder to waist 161/2"
sleeve 241/2"
